title: CNN Debate Moderator Anderson Cooper Dismisses Story Suggesting Clinton Ties
text: CNN host Anderson Cooper , the moderator of Tuesday night's Democratic presidential debate, dismissed a Weekly Standard report claiming he was a member of the Clinton Global Initiative , a story amplified on The Drudge Report in the hours
